{"tid":2273900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果天貓iPhone 12突下架 疑與螞蟻有關","createTime":"2020-11-06T05:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T16:07:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a162f71b54f541ee738c7a3cb8da62c90374db","tid":2273900,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201106/HWJPNSJVUJF77IYYBINUHMNLVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201106%2FHWJPNSJVUJF77IYYBINUHMNLVY%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8r32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=e01121b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201106%2FHWJPNSJVUJF77IYYBINUHMNLVY%2F&h=b64a6c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201106/HWJPNSJVUJF77IYYBINUHMNLVY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蘋果天貓iPhone 12突下架 疑與螞蟻有關<br />\n<br />\n蘋果天貓旗艦店的iPhone 12和iPhone 12 Pro昨突然離奇下架，沒有解釋原因。內媒《新浪科技》向內部人士求證，iPhone 12系列只是賣完了才被下架，但有網民猜測，iPhone 12系列可在天貓用螞蟻集團旗下類似信用卡的消費金融業務「花唄」分期付款有關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mz3JQGBIPflHSIDbHgGtbH6AbII=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XLJ7XDA3EVC63O6UWBHOCWBRTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fmz3JQGBIPflHSIDbHgGtbH6AbII%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXLJ7XDA3EVC63O6UWBHOCWBRTM.jpg&h=84d9d589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蘋果天貓旗艦店的iPhone 12突然離奇下架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方未有解釋原因<br />\n<br />\n雖然iPhone 12和iPhone 12 Pro在蘋果天貓旗艦店離奇被下架，但 Apple 產品在京東自家旗艦店可以購買，只是iPhone 12 Pro 則顯示為「無貨訂購」狀態。天貓旗艦店商品頁面顯示，自2020年10月21日起至2020年11月11日止，所有 iPhone 12、iPhone 12 Pro、iPad、Mac、Apple Watch及AirPods可享受「花唄」12期免息分期，但Apple在京東就沒有這句。外界估計，近日螞蟻集團煞停上市，「花唄」、「借唄」也受到關注，聯想到這可能與此有關。<br />\n<br />\n天貓沒有解釋iPhone 下架的情況，僅回應稱：「。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新浪科技"},{"pid":"27859785f4fa9f392e5fe7f5e983c6f642a89ce0","tid":2273900,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"淘寶天貓 分享<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/taobaotmall\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftaobaotmall&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8r32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=86685fd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/taobaotmall</a>"}]}